Summary: Witnessed while driving in the a.m. looked like a meteorite
divs: Sighting DetailsI was heading to work on CO. Hwy J-13 almost to Hwy 148 when i saw this green object fall straight out of the skk with an orange flame like trail. I almost thought it was a firework but the thing is no one lives around there and its not like people light fireworks at 630 in the mornign either. There could have been one other witness to the even because there was a vehicle behind me at the time. Ultimately the object fell to the ground or disappeared there.
